import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { Button, Box } from '@mui/material';

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Box 
      sx={{ 
        alignItems: 'center',
        gap: 2, 
        padding: 4,
        display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-around',flexDirection: 'column', marginTop: 2, maxWidth: 400, margin: '0 auto', gap: 2
      }}
    >
      <Box>
        <Button variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/register">
          Регистрация
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/login">
          Авторизация
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button  variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/posts">
          Новости
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button  variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/transactions">
          ТНС
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button  variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/tgks">
          ТГК
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box>
        <Button  variant="contained" color="primary" component={Link} to="/waters">
          Водоканал
        </Button>
      </Box>
    </Box>
    
  );
};

export default Home;
